msgid "**Who uses Python for serious work?**"
msgstr ""

#: ../src/Doc/howto/advocacy.rst:242
msgid ""
"Lots of people; one interesting thing about Python is the surprising "
"diversity of applications that it's been used for.  People are using Python "
"to:"
